(St Mirren) Glass (Aberdeen), McCann (Dundee), Liddell (Barnsley),
Crawford (Raith Rovers). Substitutes -- Gardner (Hibernian), Donnelly
(Celtic), Murray (Rangers), Hamilton (Dundee), McLaughlin (Celtic).
GREECE -- Karkanis, Mavrogenidis, Kiassos, Theodoridis, Macheridis,
