<DOCNO>GH950816-000013</DOCNO>
<DOCID>GH950816-000013</DOCID>
<DATE>950816</DATE>
<HEADLINE>No Headline Present</HEADLINE>
<EDITION>3</EDITION>
<PAGE>32</PAGE>
<RECORDNO>976863246</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
* JIM Fallon will take charge of Dumbarton for their Coca-Cola Cup tie
against Kilmarnock on Saturday.
With the loss of manager Murdo MacLeod to Partick Thistle, coach
Fallon will oversee the Boghead club until a new appointment is made.
</TEXT>
